			"type": "facts",
			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"title": "",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><a class=\"crossref\" id=\"84258\"></a><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Observera!</span> Kompletterande uppgifter <br>om f&ouml;rgiftningar kan erh&aring;llas fr&aring;n <br>Giftinformationscentralen</p>\r\n<p>tfn 08-736 03 84 eller<br>tfn 08-517 747 42 <br>(observera, endast f&ouml;r sjukv&aring;rden!)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
